data.description: Welcome to the listing for this gorgeous contemporary home in Loveland, CO! This one story home is situated on a desirable corner lot, and boasts three bedrooms and two bathrooms along with a 2 car garage. You'll love the central air cooling and forced air heating, perfect for keeping your home comfortable year-round. Plus, ceiling fans throughout the home provide added comfort and energy efficiency.Inside, you'll find an open floor plan and a separate dining room, perfect for hosting gatherings with friends and family. The pantry offer ample storage space for all your belongings, while the large backyard and patio provide plenty of room for outdoor relaxation and entertaining. And if that's not enough, this home also features a convenient storage building.Don't miss your chance to call this contemporary Loveland home your own. Schedule a viewing today!
